{"id":247353,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-湖南长沙县强拆受害人李巧玲夫妇因上访/","date":"2012-08-16T09:30:56Z","modified":"2012-08-16T09:30:56Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南长沙县强拆受害人李巧玲夫妇因上访被拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，湖南省长沙市长沙县被强拆户李巧玲到北京反映拆迁问题，回长沙后被长沙县公安局以“抱团集聚访”为由行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。此前李巧玲因为上访曾被拘留过。经过</span><span>两次拘留以后，李巧玲的身心受到极大的伤害，记性身体精神都比以前差多了，而且耳朵也听不太清。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，李巧玲的丈夫胡冬阳到国家信访局上访，反映拆迁问题，在问题没解决的情况下，信访事项即被终结。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，胡冬阳的上访被长沙县公安定性为“非法上访”，</span><span> </span><span>处行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日。因为胡东阳的血压较高，高压</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">195</span><span>低压</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">128</span><span>，拘留所不同意接收，长沙县跳马派出所无视病情，强行关押。胡东阳从拘留所获释后，全身发烂，血压无法降下，只好送医院急救。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，李巧玲状告长沙县公安局截访、打击报复上访人员非法拘留案在长沙开庭，作为被告的长沙县公安局的代理人当庭进行了长篇的辩护和横蛮无理的坚持。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李巧玲电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13467547907</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BapaEOeMGEI/UCyt4jZBoOI/AAAAAAAALY8/EH-SEIerccM/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BapaEOeMGEI/UCyt4jZBoOI/AAAAAAAALY8/EH-SEIerccM/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"319\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZFD9Vj4Y1i0/UCyt7dzfYJI/AAAAAAAALZE/IxMUvTqykbc/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\"